Package com.atakmap.map.layer.feature

Class AttributeSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.map.layer.feature.AttributeSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Disposable
    public final class AttributeSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements Disposable
    A strongly typed key-value pairing of metadata. Keys must be text and values are restricted to text, primitives, binary blobs, arrays of those types and nested AttributeSet instances.
